OL,3,CInspectors highlight overcrowding,
OL,4,Cdrugs and rise in self-harm at prison
OL,6,FA report has highlighted problems with
OL,7,Fovercrowding, drugs and a rise in self-
OL,8,Fharm at HMP Hull.
OL,10,FThe HM Inspectorate of Prisons visited
OL,11,Fthe prison over three days in April
OL,12,Fand found it had made progress in a
OL,13,Fnumber of areas since the last visit
OL,14,Fbut there were still areas for concern.
OL,16,FThe report found the prison remained
OL,17,F"severely overcrowded", with too many
OL,18,Fprisoners living in pairs in cells
OL,19,Fdesigned for one person.
