OL,3,CInspectors highlight overcrowding,
OL,4,Cdrugs and rise in self-harm at prison
OL,6,FIt said: "Leaders were taking steps to
OL,7,Fmitigate the experience of sharing
OL,8,Fcramped cells by extending time out of
OL,9,Fcell and enhancing the regime to
OL,10,Fencourage greater prisoner engagement.
OL,12,F"However, a significant minority of
OL,13,Fprisoners were still locked up in
OL,14,Fovercrowded conditions for more than
OL,15,F21 hours a day."
