OL,3,CInspectors highlight overcrowding,
OL,4,Cdrugs and rise in self-harm at prison
OL,6,FThe inspection found that, although
OL,7,Foverall violence levels in the prison
OL,8,Fremain low, with staff assaults
OL,9,Freducing by 40% since the last
OL,10,Finspection, self-harm at HMP Hull is
OL,11,Fon the rise.
OL,13,FIt said: "There had been one self-
OL,14,Finflicted death since the inspection
OL,15,Fand rates of self-harm had increased.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
