OL,3,CInspectors highlight overcrowding,
OL,4,Cdrugs and rise in self-harm at prison
OL,6,F"However, leaders understood the
OL,7,Ffactors contributing to this and were
OL,8,Ftaking action informed by data to
OL,9,Faddress them, including increasing
OL,10,Ftime out of cell, developing the
OL,11,Fenrichment activities offer and
OL,12,Fproviding more education, skills and
OL,13,Fwork opportunities."
