OL,3,CInspectors highlight overcrowding,
OL,4,Cdrugs and rise in self-harm at prison
OL,6,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This Government inherited a
OL,8,Fprison system in crisis ` overcrowded,
OL,9,Fwith drugs and violence rife. While we
OL,10,Fhave seen notable improvements since
OL,11,Fthe last inspection, we fully
OL,12,Facknowledge the challenges that remain
OL,13,Fat HMP Hull.
OL,15,F"We are already addressing the
OL,16,Fconcerns raised, including work to
OL,17,Fupskill staff so they can better
OL,18,Freduce the risk of self-harm. This is
OL,19,Fon top of landmark sentencing reforms
OL,20,Fannounced last week to reduce pressure
OL,21,Fon our prisons."
